  <scopecontent id="aspace_b4dcdc48e8a0ef9f7f07adff284cfdd8">
    <head>COLLECTION DESCRIPTION</head>
<p>Correspondence, minutes, accounts, inventories, archaeological notes, programs, and printed material; department chairman was Frederick O. Waage. Organizations represented include the American Numismatic Society, the Archaeological Institute of America, and the College Art Association of America. Major correspondents include Cornelius William De Kiewiet, and Deane W. Malott.</p>  </scopecontent>
